OL,3,CWho controls my local council in
OL,4,CLondon?
OL,6,FAbove all of this sits the Greater
OL,7,FLondon Authority, led by the Mayor of
OL,8,FLondon. The Mayor handles city-wide
OL,9,Fissues such as transport (through
OL,10,FTransport for London), policing
OL,11,Foversight, fire services, and London-
OL,12,Fwide planning strategy.
OL,14,FPut simply: boroughs run your
OL,15,Fneighbourhood. The Mayor runs the
OL,16,Fcapital.
